The paper is about face verification using Convolutional Neural Networks, which is a popular topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also proposes two strategies for training using normalized features, which involves optimization and mathematical analysis, indicating a focus on machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). Additionally, the paper mentions the LFW dataset, which is commonly used in multimedia (cs.MM) and neural network (cs.NE) research.
